column1: What is your present religion, if any?
column4: How often do you: Pray in public with visible motions (sign of the cross, bowing, prostration, shokeling, etc)
column5: How often do you: Pray in public using some kind of physical object (rosary, tefillin, etc)
column6: How often do you: Pray aloud before meals in the presence of people who don't belong to your religion
column7: How often do you: Tell someone you'll pray for him or her
column8: How often do you: Ask or offer to pray with someone
column9: How often do you: Bring up your religion, unprompted, in conversation
column10: How often do you: Ask others about their religion, unprompted, in conversation
column11: How often do you: Decline some kind of food or beverage for religious reasons (kosher, halal, fasting rules, etc)
column12: How often do you: Wear religious clothing/jewelry (hijab, kippah, wig, kara, turban, cross, etc)
column13: How often do you: Participate in a public religious event on the streets (Corpus Christi procession, inauguration of Torah scrolls, etc)
column16: How much total combined money did all members of your HOUSEHOLD earn last year?
